---
title: Honey-Soy Glazed Chicken & Sesame Fries with Crispy Shallots
description: When honey, soy sauce and a hot pan collide you get these deliciously caramelised chicken thighs. Serve them with a refreshing Japanese-style salad and crispy sesame fries – just the thing for soaking up any extra sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-soy-glazed-chicken-thights-d3d1f865.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/honey-soy-glazed-chicken-thights-5bcea479ae08b50a8467aba2-27589cef.pdf
